= mixiapp_base

Ruby on Rails plugin for Mixi OpenSocial Gadget based on peeled-unshiu mixi plugin
(http://wiki.unshiu.jp/)

Sorry, but this document is not completed.

== Installation

 git clone git://github.com/araimotoki/mixiapp_base.git

The following gems and their dependencies are required by this client library: 
* oauth
* json
* gettext (optional, for gettext)
* mocha (optional, for running tests) 

 sudo rake gem:install

Edit configration files:
* config/database.yml
* config/app.yml

Create DB:
 rake db:create
 rake db:migrate

== Usage

Your gadget application url is:
 http://your.domain/gadget.xml


